# PRD.md — Product Requirements Document

---

## Problem

Most habit trackers give users a rigid daily checklist. When life gets busy — midnight hangouts, pitching events, packed weekends — users miss habits, break streaks, and give up. The app never adapts to real life.

---

## Solution

Users describe their week in plain natural language. The AI Coach reads their schedule, understands their energy levels, and generates a realistic habit plan that fits around their actual life — then fills it into a calendar automatically.

---

## Target Users

| User | Description |
|---|---|
| Free User | Students trying habit tracking for the first time |
| Premium User | Professionals/students with complex, unpredictable schedules |
| Admin | Platform operator managing users and subscriptions |

---

## User Stories

### Free User
- As a free user, I can register and log in securely
- As a free user, I can create up to 3 habits
- As a free user, I can mark habits as complete each day
- As a free user, I can see my current streak per habit
- As a free user, I can see a basic dashboard of my progress
- As a free user, I can upgrade to Premium

### Premium User
- As a premium user, I can do everything a free user can
- As a premium user, I can create unlimited habits
- As a premium user, I can chat with the AI Coach in natural language
- As a premium user, the AI Coach reads my schedule and generates a habit plan
- As a premium user, the AI-generated plan auto-fills my in-app calendar
- As a premium user, I can connect my Google Calendar for two-way sync via MCP
- As a premium user, I can see the leaderboard and compete with others
- As a premium user, I receive a daily AI-generated motivational tip
- As a premium user, if I miss a habit the AI automatically reschedules it

### Admin
- As an admin, I can view all users and their subscription tiers
- As an admin, I can manually upgrade or downgrade a user's subscription
- As an admin, I can deactivate or delete user accounts
- As an admin, I can manage habit categories available to all users
- As an admin, I can view platform analytics (DAU, habit completion rates, premium count)

---

## Features In Scope (MVP)

- [x] Auth — register, login, logout, JWT
- [x] Role system — free, premium, admin
- [x] Habit CRUD — create, read, update, delete habits
- [x] Daily habit logging — mark complete, view history
- [x] Streak tracking — consecutive day counter
- [x] AI Coach chat — natural language schedule input
- [x] AI habit plan generation — outputs structured plan
- [x] In-app calendar — weekly view with AI-filled events
- [x] Google Calendar sync — via MCP (premium only)
- [x] Leaderboard — weekly points ranking (premium only)
- [x] Dashboard — progress rings, streak display
- [x] Admin panel — user management, subscription control
- [x] Subscription gating — enforce free vs premium server-side

## Features Out of Scope (Future)

- [ ] Mobile app
- [ ] Real payment processing (Stripe) — admin manually upgrades for now
- [ ] Apple Calendar sync
- [ ] Social features (follow friends, share habits)
- [ ] Push notifications

