## UI/UX Vision

- **Tropical Punch** theme: warm mango orange (#FF8243), soft pink (#FFC0CB), sunny yellow (#FCE883), ocean teal (#069494)
- Warm cream (#FFF9F5) backgrounds with deep navy (#1A1A2E) dark mode
- Satisfying checkmark animation on habit completion (orange → teal transition)
- Streak flame that pulses between orange and yellow, grows with consecutive days
- Smooth leaderboard number animations
- Teal progress rings on dashboard
- Chat bubble interface for AI Coach (orange for user, teal for AI)
- Calendar animates as AI fills in the plan (teal event blocks)
- Angular Animations + GSAP for all transitions
- UI UX Pro Max skill for professional design intelligence